item.description:
Usage In order to use Hugo Pipes function on an asset file containing Go Template magic the function resources.ExecuteAsTemplate must be used.
The function takes three arguments: the target path for the created resource, the template context, and the resource object.
// assets/sass/template.scss $backgroundColor: {{ .Param &#34;backgroundColor&#34; }}; $textColor: {{ .Param &#34;textColor&#34; }}; body{ background-color:$backgroundColor; color: $textColor; } // [...] {{ $sassTemplate := resources.Get &#34;sass/template.scss&#34; }} {{ $style := $sassTemplate | resources.
